================================================================================

Subject to the negotiated terms, a commercial licence usually grants:

  * The right to use, modify, and distribute Kaption source and binaries
    in proprietary / closed-source products and services.

  * Exemption from the AGPL-3.0 obligation to release derivative-work
    source code.

  * Optional: contractual warranty, indemnity, and support terms.

  * Optional: a limited trademark licence to use the "Kaption" name
    and logo in specific contexts (granted case-by-case).

