================================================================================
HOW TO REQUEST A COMMERCIAL LICENCE
================================================================================

Email:   hello@kaption.one
Website: https://kaption.one

When you write, please include:

  * Your name, organisation, and country of operation.
  * A short description of how you intend to use Kaption — many uses
    fit AGPL-3.0, and we will tell you if a commercial licence is
    actually unnecessary.
  * Estimated number of seats, installations, or end users covered.
  * Whether you need a warranty, indemnity, support, or trademark
    licence in addition to the source-licence exemption.

We aim to reply within a few business days and finalise most
agreements within two weeks.

